{"tid":220132,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"連二人世間都變到好難","createTime":"2017-04-27T17:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T17:32:09.000Z","uid":4244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e104570843dadcb1aee956c94ca72075f09773d","tid":220132,"uid":4244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:30:07.000Z","msg":"本身諗住請兩日假連埋勞動節同你周圍去玩下 已經推哂所有朋友<br />\n重買埋小禮物 諗住可以開開心心咁過呢四日假期<br />\n結果你同我講 你問你個同學一唔一齊去 結果變左三人行<br />\n可能係我一開始就誤會左只係得我地兩個人<br />\n放假之前一日又同我講 會多幾個人 重要全女班 <br />\n我個下除左講你地玩得開心啲 都無第二句好講<br />\n請哂假 諗住全程同你兩個人二人世間 可以修補一下關係<br />\n結果就自己一個過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54998e7d8011e10112936248d38db90c8c57417c","tid":220132,"uid":6294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:30:48.000Z","msg":"世界呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a63f541e8e3c3cb54ca04256623b91af7b3047","tid":220132,"uid":4244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:31:33.000Z","msg":"自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  世界"},{"pid":"c913df8a65d31f1ed3bf4401817d7d516d4c307d","tid":220132,"uid":4244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:32:09.000Z","msg":"灰到打錯字都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}